token_lists.title: MonoPrint
token_lists.description:
Monoprinting is a type of printmaking where the intent is to make unique prints, that may explore an image serially.
Other methods of printmaking create editioned multiples, the monoprint is editioned as 1 of 1
That's why it's so rare.

token_lists.title: HyperHalo
token_lists.description: At the end of the Anthropocene alien life form took advantage of digitally embodied humans embroiled in a technologically facilitated Singularity.  Hyper stratification and data dependencies that emerged from artificially enhanced co-existence led to a neo-modernity  controlled by extra-terrestrial Overlords, robotic Sentinels and replicant Symbiotics.The Symbiosis project sought to create an artificial intelligence that could be used as a "helper" for human beings while still maintaining its own independence. The AI would have no direct contact with humans except via proxy machines such as personal computers and digital assistants, but it would provide the equivalent of an Internet of Things connection to ensure non-sentient life forms could flourish. Read more at https://alexanderhayes.medium.com/
